<h1>ONLINE COURSES:</h1>
<p>An online class is a course conducted over the Internet.<br>
 They are generally conducted through a learning management system,<br> 
in which students can view their course syllabus and academic progress,<br>
 as well as communicate with fellow students and their course instructor.
</p>
