<h1 style="color:blue;text-align:center;">ADVANTAGES AND DISADVANTAGES OF ONLINE COURSES</h1>
<p style="color:maroon;">Learning is often considered to be a normal part of working and personal life.<br>
 Both learning for achieving a job as well as for achieving knowledge should not be neglected.<br>
 Online environment is changing continuously and it represents a great opportunity for learning. <br>
It is very important to discover how to learn using all available communication channels<br>
